OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBreezy
OL,6,Ftonight with clear spells and
OL,7,Foccasional showers moving through,
OL,8,Fthese could be heavy at times and
OL,9,Fmerging into longer spells of rain for
OL,10,Fa time overnight. Staying mild with
OL,11,Fthe brisk winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FLargely dry with sunny
OL,14,Fspells though the odd shower still
OL,15,Fpossible. Turning cloudier into the
OL,16,Fafternoon with more persistent rain
OL,17,Farriving by the evening. Winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
